===Etymology===
The first word of the [[introit]] for the traditional requiem mass, an alternative [[accusative case]] of {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|requiēs||rest, repose|lang=la}}, from {{term|re-||again|lang=la}} + {{term|quiēs||rest, quiet|lang=la}}.

